## Getting started

### Set up and acivate python virtual env

``` bash
python3 -m venv env
source env/bin/activate
```

### Install dependencies

``` bash
pip install nbdev pre-commit
pip install -e '.[dev]'
```

### Install pre-commit hooks for nbdev prep and cleanup

``` bash
pre-commit install
```
